{"tid":1234001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奉勸各位諗清楚目前嘅狀況 認清事實","createTime":"2019-06-17T00:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T02:03:49.000Z","uid":54381,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"66dfa9446e9c2a9915aa68630bea1fc8b610faa0","tid":1234001,"uid":54381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:08:05.000Z","msg":"依家政府明顯想拖字訣黎令我地主動消耗民怨<br />\n人類總會響等唔到回應嘅時候失落<br />\n繼而失去動力 最後就會變返成盤散沙<br />\n呢個就係政府想得到嘅結果<br />\n<br />\n咁我地有冇野可以做？<br />\n有 我地需要去慢慢教育返呢班啱啱醒覺嘅人<br />\n同佢地慢慢滲透依家嘅政權繼續漠視佢地嘅訴求<br />\n去引導佢地到底導致今日嘅狀況到底係咩原因<br />\n<br />\n唔響心態上改變佢地 係好難贏到呢場仗<br />\n呢個係意識形態嘅問題<br />\n人地老共用左20年甚至更多時間去滲透<br />\n你以為集結到200萬人遊行幾次就有用？<br />\n如果你真係咁諗嘅就未免太天真<br />\n你地需要重新去理解中國嘅戰術 - 超限戰<br />\n<br />\n重申一次 我地面對緊嘅係最難搞嘅對手<br />\n唔好再用咁天真嘅態度去諗<br />\n如果唔係就真係玩完"},{"pid":"70ba997103bf2e46bf9739db1db2d2890fe0904d","tid":1234001,"uid":54381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:14:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69e720108d584dd6566c0ea039f24b85a1f3919","tid":1234001,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e761a4180b2ae82e5d6400bbf728daf5184d12","tid":1234001,"uid":54381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:18:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ef72010a88ae8a52093928687ea541ad64ea3e","tid":1234001,"uid":54381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90565aec03328a79a59fadce9a3c6091d4f8dc7","tid":1234001,"uid":54381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:33:21.000Z","msg":"大家認真聽我講一講<br />\n你地只係召喚到200萬人<br />\n但係未令200萬人企埋同一陣線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2d0443092a9ce1e0ade0c4236a2b960f401ed4","tid":1234001,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:34:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我知係拖所以我地要團結屌777直至撤回條例同釋放義士</span></span>"},{"pid":"63f60e8c48c5da1f31de7f2b237a54ec0274b19b","tid":1234001,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:38:58.000Z","msg":"仲有係推呢兩百萬人都出嚟投票，真正踢走保皇黨<br />\n今次犯民都已經改變態度，願意主動去癱瘓立法會先至令個條例過唔到，必須要將非保皇黨送晒入立法會"},{"pid":"2951fd85b31f48dbbc8a28919ded1d8c3a0ced58","tid":1234001,"uid":54381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:54:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ce107671976e64de1784b47672499b8a312785","tid":1234001,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:59:50.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"844cd7d2d3a07537b6d8c9a496a83ee2a616b97d","tid":1234001,"uid":232220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:02:37.000Z","msg":"同時認清一個事實<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zUqXPJD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzUqXPJD.png&h=26336346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府用詞曖昧 我們拒被矇騙<br />\n<br />\nNO PAUSE NO SUSPEND<br />\nWE NEED WITHDRAW"},{"pid":"9a92e9157f45b412463b94726e1c413f8f9fa26e","tid":1234001,"uid":54381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"844cd7d2d3a07537b6d8c9a496a83ee2a616b97d","tid":1234001,"uid":232220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:02:37.000Z","msg":"同時認清一個事實<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zUqXPJD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzUqXPJD.png&h=26336346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府用詞曖昧 我們拒被矇騙<br />\n<br />\nNO PAUSE NO SUSPEND<br />\nWE NEED WITHDRAW"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:06:05.000Z","msg":"冇錯 大家根本未贏到任何野<br />\n我地只係換黎左敵人拖延嘅時間<